<p><strong>Additional Contributions:</strong> We thank all the previous and current Medicare Patient Safety Monitoring System team members for their contributions to this work, including Deron Galusha, MS (statistician at the Yale University School of Medicine), for his contribution to crosswalk all the numbers, figures, and tables reported in the study. We also thank Dennis Wagner, MPA (formerly of the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services [CMS]), for his contributions to patient safety improvement during much of the period of this study as well as Jeff Floyd, BS, Sean Warner, MBA, PMP, CSM, and the entire team at the CMS Clinical Data Abstraction Center (under the oversight of the TISTA Science &amp; Technology Corporation), for their work over the decade. Mr Galusha was compensated for his contribution but the other named persons were not compensated.</p>
